title: Why Is this happening?
body: I was just playing on my New Account since my old one ive created couple of years ago. was unaccesable because of various reasons. and i realised my name changed. but then it changed back. and then it changed to that other again. my Summoner name Used to be "Wood Division 5" But for some Reason it Keeps changes to This weird Stuff: " IS134C72BD619BF5 " and i honestly dont know what to do about that

replies.body:
1. German forums.
2. I think that's the name you get when the player support changes due to inappropiate name. Go and message the support and ask them.
